                     <text>
                        <paragraph>Vitafol<sup>®</sup>-Plus is available as a purple, oval shaped softgel capsule imprinted EV0092. Available in Box of Unit-Dose pack of 30 (5 child resistant blister cards of 6 softgel capsules) (NDC0642-0092-30), and as professional samples (NDC0642-0092-01). Store at room temperature, approximately 15°-30°C (59°-86°F). Avoid excessive heat, moisture and protect from light.</paragraph>
                     </text>
